.git
.gitignore

# CMake / build (patterns need **/ to match at any depth in .dockerignore)
**/build/
**/Build/
**/build-*/
**/CMakeCache.txt
**/CMakeFiles/
**/CMakeUserPresets.json
**/cmake_install.cmake
**/compile_commands.json

# vcpkg
**/vcpkg_installed/

# Generated protobuf / gRPC sources — regenerated inside the image
**/*.pb.*
**/*.grpc.pb.*
**/*_pb2*.py
client/robot_client/generated/

# Python
**/__pycache__/
**/*.egg-info/
**/.pytest_cache/
client/.venv/

# Docs / Claude tooling
.claude/
claude_instructions/
CLAUDE.md
